\title{Field automorphism}
\author{alex-nelson}
\import{notation}
\date{2025-12-22}
\taxon{definition}

\p{Let #{\kk} be a field. An \define{Automorphism} of #{\kk} is a field isomorphism #{\sigma\colon\kk\to\kk}.}

\p{We denote by #{\Aut(\kk)} the group of all field automorphisms of #{\kk} equipped with function composition.}